<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
            integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC"
            crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link href="css/common.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="css/home.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <title>Document</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        {{!-- 헤더 --}}
        <header
            class="p-3 bg-dark text-white"
            style="user-select: auto; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <div class="container" style="user-select: auto;">
                <div
                    class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start"
                    style="user-select: auto;">
                    <a
                        href="/"
                        class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2 mb-lg-0 text-white text-decoration-none"
                        style="user-select: auto;">
                        <svg
                            class="bi me-2"
                            width="40"
                            height="32"
                            role="img"
                            aria-label="Bootstrap"
                            style="user-select: auto;">
                            <use xlink:href="#bootstrap" style="user-select: auto;"></use>
                        </svg>
                    </a>

                    <ul
                        class="nav col-12 col-lg-auto me-lg-auto mb-2 justify-content-center mb-md-0 left-menu-conatiner"
                        style="user-select: auto;">
                        <li style="user-select: auto;">
                            <a href="/" class="nav-link px-2" style="user-select: auto;">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        {{!-- <li style="user-select: auto;">
                            <a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-white" style="user-select: auto;">Features</a>
                        </li>
                        <li style="user-select: auto;">
                            <a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-white" style="user-select: auto;">Pricing</a>
                        </li>
                        <li style="user-select: auto;">
                            <a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-white" style="user-select: auto;">FAQs</a>
                        </li>
                        <li style="user-select: auto;">
                            <a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-white" style="user-select: auto;">About</a>
                        </li> --}}
                    </ul>

                    <div class="text-end" style="user-select: auto;">
                        {{#if isLogin}}
                            {{!-- TODO: 로그아웃 엔드포인트로 요청 --}}
                            <button
                                type="button"
                                id="logout-btn"
                                class="btn btn-outline-light me-2"
                                style="user-select: auto; font-weight: bold;">로그아웃</button>
                        {{/if}}
                        {{#unless isLogin}}
                            <button
                                type="button"
                                id="login-signup-btn"
                                class="btn btn-outline-light me-2"
                                style="user-select: auto; font-weight: bold;">직원 로그인</button>
                        {{/unless}}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        {{!-- 선택 --}}
        <div class="container">
            <div class="jumbotron" style="user-select: auto;">
                <h1 style="user-select: auto;">프로젝트를 맡겨보세요</h1>
                <p class="lead" style="user-select: auto; word-break:keep-all;">
                    어떤 프로젝트든 해결할 수 있습니다. 작든 크든 크기에 상관 없이 신속하고 정확하게 프로젝트를 완성해드립니다. 머릿 속에 있는 그대로 결과물을
                    우리의 프로젝트를 만든다는 마음으로 만들어드립니다.
                </p>
                <p style="user-select: auto; margin-top: 50px;">
                    <a
                        class="btn btn-lg btn-success"
                        href="#"
                        role="button"
                        style="user-select: auto;">프로젝트 상담하러 가기</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.min.js"></script>
        <script src="/javascript/home.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>